thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Fine Made Electronics Group sees 2017 net profit up 40 pct to 50 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Fine Made Electronics Group sees 2017 net profit up 40 pct to 50 pct

organizations.name: shenzhen fine made electronics group co ltd

text:
Jan 23(Reuters) - Shenzhen Fine Made Electronics Group Co Ltd
* Sees 2017 net profit to increase by 40 percent to 50 percent, or to be 53.8 million yuan to 57.7 million yuan
* Says 2016 net profit was 38.5 million yuan
* Says that increased income of main business and gross margin as main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/e2JR55
